<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q54_v2" title="Q54_v2" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceC</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>En un pictograma (no mostrado aquí) se registraron los medios de transporte preferidos para ir al colegio. Cada ícono representa a 2 personas y, en total, el pictograma representa a 50 personas. En la tabla adjunta se indica cuántos íconos corresponden a cada medio de transporte.</p>
    <div>
      <table>
        <tr>
          <th>Medio de transporte</th>
          <th>Cantidad de íconos</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Bus</td>
          <td>8</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Bicicleta</td>
          <td>4</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Automóvil</td>
          <td>3</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Metro</td>
          <td>5</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Caminar</td>
          <td>5</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>Si se elige a una de estas personas al azar, ¿cuál es la probabilidad de que use bus o metro como medio de transporte principal?</qti-prompt>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>8</m:mn>
            <m:mn>25</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Bus corresponde a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> personas y metro corresponde a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> personas. Entonces, bus o metro reúne <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>26</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> personas de <m:math><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:math>, por lo que la probabilidad es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>26</m:mn><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> = <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>13</m:mn><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>12</m:mn>
            <m:mn>25</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La cantidad de personas que usa bus o metro es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>26</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Sobre un total de <m:math><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:math> personas, la probabilidad es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>26</m:mn><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> = <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>13</m:mn><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>. Además, <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> = <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>24</m:mn><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, y <m:math><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:math> no es igual a <m:math><m:mn>26</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>13</m:mn>
            <m:mn>25</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Bus corresponde a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> personas y metro a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> personas. Entonces, usan bus o metro <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>26</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> personas de un total de <m:math><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:math>. La probabilidad es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>26</m:mn><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> = <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>13</m:mn><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            <m:mn>5</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La probabilidad pedida considera bus o metro. Eso corresponde a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>26</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> personas de <m:math><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:math>, es decir, <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>26</m:mn><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> = <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>13</m:mn><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>. En cambio, <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> = <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, y <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math> no es igual a <m:math><m:mn>26</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Convertir íconos a personas</strong></p>
            <p>Cada ícono representa a 2 personas.</p>
            <p>Bus: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> personas.</p>
            <p>Metro: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> personas.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Sumar las personas que usan bus o metro</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>26</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces, 26 personas usan bus o metro como medio de transporte principal.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Usar el total de personas</strong></p>
            <p>El pictograma representa a 50 personas en total.</p>
            <p>La probabilidad es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>26</m:mn><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Simplificar la fracción</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>26</m:mn><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> se simplifica dividiendo numerador y denominador por <m:math><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>26</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>50</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mfrac></m:math> = <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>13</m:mn><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La probabilidad de elegir al azar a una persona que use bus o metro es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>13</m:mn><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la <strong>C</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>